cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.IR 

This paper is about using generative adversarial networks (GANs) to generate labeled samples for data augmentation in remote sensing image scene classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.GR (Graphics), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
